OL,4,CAt risk Afghan journalists to be
OL,5,Coffered UK relocation
OL,6, Afghan journalists who work for the
OL,7, British media will be allowed to
OL,8, relocate to the UK if they are under
OL,9, "imminent threat" from the Taliban, the
OL,10, foreign secretary has said.
OL,12,FIn a letter to UK media organisations,
OL,13,FDominic Raab said cases would be
OL,14,Fconsidered "on an exceptional basis".
OL,16,FBritish news outlets had urged No 10 to
OL,17,Ftreat Afghan journalists the same as
OL,18,Fthe British Army's Afghan interpreters.
OL,20,FIt comes as a top Afghan media officer
OL,21,Fwas killed by the Taliban on Friday.
